Monster Challenger			KEY:Trait ~ Monster Challenger	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.CombatTrait				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Monster Challenger]								SOURCEPAGE:p.3		DESC:You have made it your mission to bring down a fearsome beast. Choose two of the following: aberrations, animals, dragons, fey, magical beasts, oozes, and vermin. You can move at full speed without penalty while using Survival to follow tracks left by your chosen creature types.																BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Monster Challenger Trait Choice|2
