Monster Survivor				KEY:Trait ~ Monster Survivor		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.CombatTrait				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Monster Survivor]								SOURCEPAGE:p.3		DESC:You've escaped with your life after a terrible monster attack. You gain a +4 dodge bonus to AC against attacks of opportunity made against you by Large or larger opponents when you're making a withdraw action.

